{{glossary}}
{{term|[[A roll]]}}
{{defn|}}
{{term|[[Above-the-line (filmmaking)|above-the-line]]}}
{{defn|The list of individuals who guide and influence the creative direction, process, and voice of a given narrative in a film and related expenditures. These roles include but are not limited to the {{gli|screenwriter}}, {{gli|producer}}, {{gli|director}}, and {{gli|actor|actors}}. Contrast ''{{gli|below-the-line}}''.<ref>{{cite journal|title=Film & TV Production Roles and Departments|url=http://film.vic.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0010/4897/Crew-Roles-and-Departments-Guide.pdf|accessdate=21 October 2014|format=PDF}}</ref>}}
{{term|accelerated montage}}
{{defn|}}
{{term|accent light}}
{{defn|}}
