{{defn|The first version of a given {{gli|motion picture}} that is printed to film after [[color correction]] on an {{gli|interpositive}}. It is also the first version of the movie printed to film with the sound properly synced to the picture.<ref>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/26857/answer-print Answer Print] at ''Encyclopædia Britannica''</ref>}}
