{{Infobox video game |title = NET:Zone |image = |developer = [[Compro Games]] |publisher = [[GameTek]] |genre = [[Adventure game]] |modes = [[Single player]] |released = 1996 |platforms = [[MS-DOS]], [[Microsoft Windows]] }}
'''''Netzone''''', stylized as '''''NET:Zone''''', is computer game developed by [[Compro Games]] and published by [[GameTek]] in 1996 for the PC. It is a cyberpunk, puzzle, click adventure game wherein the player explores a 3D cyberspace environment created by a company named Cycorp.<ref>https://www.mobygames.com/game/netzone/mobyrank</ref>
